Sears to sell Kenmore brand on Amazon
Sears Holdings Corp. will start selling its Kenmore line of refrigerators and stoves on Amazon.com Inc.'s website, marking the first distribution of its kitchen appliances outside of its own stores. Sears's shares rose 15% to $10 in morning trading, bringing the stock into positive-trading territory this year.

Jul. 20, 2017 at 12:05 p.m. ET
by MarketWatch









Stanley Black & Decker board hikes dividend
Stanley Black & Decker Inc.  late Wednesday said its board raised the quarterly dividend by nearly 9%. The 5-cents-a-share hike makes for a dividend of 63 cents a share to be paid Sept. 19 to shareholders of record as of Sept. 1. Shares of Stanley Black & Decker were unchanged after hours.

Jul. 19, 2017 at 6:34 p.m. ET
by Wallace Witkowski









